# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __iadd__, __isub__, __imul__ across all 6 decimal subjects
#
# 6 classes x 3 methods = 18 rows.
# All eighteen values are false. KEY FINDING: Decimal defines __add__,
# __sub__, __mul__, __radd__, __rsub__, __rmul__ but NOT the in-place
# variants (__iadd__, __isub__, __imul__). Decimal instances are immutable;
# augmented assignment (d += x, d -= x, d *= x) rebinds the variable to a
# new Decimal via the forward operator, it does not mutate d in place.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

